Turns over very slowly
and these terminals,

00:15:26.760 --> 00:15:31.100
these boutons come in,
plug in, in between.

00:15:31.100 --> 00:15:33.830
So this is, how would you say,

00:15:33.830 --> 00:15:36.750
data that is headed in the direction

00:15:36.750 --> 00:15:40.240
I think, of strongly
supporting Roger's postulate.

00:15:40.240 --> 00:15:44.660
All of this is unpublished,
but I think it's exciting.

00:15:44.660 --> 00:15:48.010
It's the product of, I
think, great thinking

00:15:48.010 --> 00:15:50.420
by many investigators, great colleagues,

00:15:50.420 --> 00:15:53.073
great collaborators, generous support.

00:15:53.073 --> 00:15:56.632
This is the cast of characters,
